Vaulted ceilings make the home feel even more spacious. Beautifully designed kitchen overlooks the living area creating an open concept. Granite countertops and contemporary cabinets in the kitchen- Not age restricted and NO LOT FEES. You own the land. This is a must see that is close to shopping, restaurants, and nightlife. This is a MUST-SEE!
